'''肯尼斯·洛勒根'''（{{lang-en|Kenneth Lonergan}}，{{bd|1962年|10月16日}}）是一名[[美國|美國]]男劇作家、編劇、導演與演員。2002年，他憑《[[紐約黑幫|紐約黑幫]]》提名了[[奧斯卡最佳原創劇本獎|奧斯卡最佳原創劇本獎]]。2016年的《[[海边的曼彻斯特|海边的曼彻斯特]]》获得[[奥斯卡最佳原創劇本獎|奥斯卡最佳原創劇本獎]]、最佳导演提名，[[金球奖最佳剧情片|金球奖最佳剧情片]]、最佳导演提名，以及[[英国电影学院奖最佳影片|英国电影学院奖最佳影片]]、最佳导演提名；赢得奥斯卡和英国电影学院奖最佳原创剧本奖。

== 早期生活 ==
肯尼斯·洛勒根出生於[[布朗克斯|布朗克斯]]。他的母親是[[猶太人|猶太人]]<ref>{{cite web|first=Rebecca|last=Mead|url=https://www.newyorker.com/magazine/2016/11/07/the-cinematic-traumas-of-kenneth-lonergan|title=The Cinematic Traumas of Kenneth Lonergan|work=The New Yorker|date=November 7, 2016|accessdate=April 25, 2018|archive-date=2021-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128154940/https://www.newyorker.com/magazine/2016/11/07/the-cinematic-traumas-of-kenneth-lonergan|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.tabletmag.com/jewish-arts-and-culture/theater-and-dance/187288/tavi-gevinson-kenneth-lonergan|title=‘This Is Our Youth' Portrays the ‘Pathetic Remnants of Upper West Side Jewish Liberalism’|accessdate=2019-01-16|date=2014-12-03|work=Tablet Magazine|archive-date=2019-09-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190909005222/https://www.tabletmag.com/jewish-arts-and-culture/theater-and-dance/187288/tavi-gevinson-kenneth-lonergan|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.npr.org/2016/11/30/503865472/manchester-by-the-sea-director-probes-the-drama-and-humor-of-grief|title='Manchester By The Sea' Director Probes The Drama And Humor Of Grief|accessdate=2019-01-16|date=2016-11-30|work=National Public Radio|archive-date=2020-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126191557/https://www.npr.org/2016/11/30/503865472/manchester-by-the-sea-director-probes-the-drama-and-humor-of-grief|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而父親是[[愛爾蘭人|愛爾蘭人]]的後裔<ref name=NY>{{cite web|url=http://www.newyorker.com/online/blogs/movies/2012/03/an-interview-with-kenneth-lonergan-about-margaret.html|work=[[The_New_Yorker|The New Yorker]]|title=Kenneth Lonergan|date=2012-03-15|first=Richard|last=Brody|access-date=2016-11-21|archive-date=2014-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140201220751/http://www.newyorker.com/online/blogs/movies/2012/03/an-interview-with-kenneth-lonergan-about-margaret.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 個人生活 ==
洛勒根的妻子是女演員{{le|J·史密斯-卡梅倫|J. Smith-Cameron}}，兩人於2000年成婚。他們有一個女兒妮爾森（Nellie）<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.csmonitor.com/2001/1005/p18s1-almp.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2016-11-21 |archive-date=2019-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191201004528/https://www.csmonitor.com/2001/1005/p18s1-almp.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.broadway.com/buzz/141223/whats-up-j-smith-cameron-the-starry-star-on-life-art-and-why-she-loves-ben-brantley/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2016-11-21 |archive-date=2020-08-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200809152621/https://www.broadway.com/buzz/141223/whats-up-j-smith-cameron-the-starry-star-on-life-art-and-why-she-loves-ben-brantley/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

